{"tid":177752,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"高價投地，股東埋單","createTime":"2017-03-29T05:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T12:50:35.000Z","uid":35505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8947ce1e89060551e2269d5f65a08e5937c10e8c","tid":177752,"uid":35505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:27:03.000Z","msg":"一貫海航手法<br />\n<br />\n利申係因為share htc個news republic, 所以變咗tvb news<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://newscdn.newsrep.net/h5/nrshare.html?r=3&amp;lan=zh_HK&amp;pid=14&amp;id=htabff6acmq_hk&amp;app_lan=&amp;mcc=454&amp;declared_lan=zh_HK&amp;pubaccount=ocms_0&amp;referrer=200620&amp;showall=1&amp;mcc=454\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewscdn.newsrep.net%2Fh5%2Fnrshare.html%3Fr%3D3%26lan%3Dzh_HK%26pid%3D14%26id%3Dhtabff6acmq_hk%26app_lan%3D%26mcc%3D454%26declared_lan%3Dzh_HK%26pubaccount%3Docms_0%26referrer%3D200620%26showall%3D1%26mcc%3D454&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a490d181\" target=\"_blank\">http://newscdn.newsrep.net/h5/nrshare.html?r=3&amp;lan=zh_HK&amp;pid=14&amp;id=htabff6acmq_hk&amp;app_lan=&amp;mcc=454&amp;declared_lan=zh_HK&amp;pubaccount=ocms_0&amp;referrer=200620&amp;showall=1&amp;mcc=454</a><br />\n<br />\n香港國際建設供股集資逾90億元<br />\n<br />\nMarch 29, 2017, 1:26 am<br />\n<br />\n海航集團子公司香港國際建設，投得兩幅啟德住宅地後，供股集資逾90億元。<br />\n<br />\n香港國際建設建議以1供2的比例供股，每股作價4.08元，較星期二收市，有近百分之1溢價，集資逾92億元，用來支付部分啟德兩幅地皮的價格。"},{"pid":"60c3fc6af4c9f916af263811426a2cc80b97e7e4","tid":177752,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:43:59.000Z","msg":"前排出左POST講呢間野<br />\n係啟德圈地 3塊地仲勁過自己市值"},{"pid":"87213cbef9a06b945ad2ed0f415971090f7ef240","tid":177752,"uid":35505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前排出左POST講呢間野<br />\n係啟德圈地 3塊地仲勁過自己市值</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啲大陸公司連向銀行融資都廢事做，直接供股搵股東出數<br />\n好撚似啲暴發戶球會咁，叫老細科水掃貨買人"},{"pid":"42830124210bf2e19f0790bff6edb8a922724edd","tid":177752,"uid":